# Summary

- There are 2 ways to dectect and measure distance between objets or human.
  
  1. Using prepared 'Haar Cascade' with opencv.
  2. Using trained 'Yolo' 

- Flask API to display opencv (camera streaming)

# 1. Using prepared 'Haar Cascade' with opencv.

## reference

- https://github.com/Asadullah-Dal17/Distance_measurement_using_single_camera.git

- https://webnautes.tistory.com/1352

# 2. Using trained 'Yolo'

## reference

- https://github.com/Asadullah-Dal17/Yolov4-Detector-and-Distance-Estimator


